            <h4>How to get there</h4>
            <p>Located at the heart of Metro Manila, one can get to Makati through the following:</p>
            <p>By land - The city has four MRT stations (Guadalupe, Buendia, Ayala, and Magallanes). Provincial and city buses ply through EDSA daily. Taxis and numerous jeepney routes also connect Makati to other Metro Manila cities.</p>
            <p>By air - The city is just 15-30 minutes away from the Ninoy Aquino International Airport.</p>
            <p>By sea -The city is 30-45 minutes away from the Port of Manila.</p>
